			<img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Kathy-Leissner-Whitman-scaled.jpg" title="Restoring the Voice of Kathy Leissner Whitman, the Texas Tower Sniper’s First Victim">
